  "title": "✅ [Personal Development]  JUNIOR SALES AMBASSADOR ✅",
  "description": "<p>📍<strong>53A Boat Quay</strong></p><p>⏰ <strong>Full-Timer [5 Weekdays + 1 Weekend]</strong></p><p>🎓 <strong>Fresh Graduates | 🫡 ORD | 🔄 Career Switchers</strong></p><p><br />✅ <strong>About Us ✅:</strong></p><p>We are one of the prime organisations that works with different industries of clients, to promote a given product or service of a given client. We focus on face-to-face marketing to interact with our customers at a deeper level, to understand their needs and to answer any enquiries.</p><p>📝 <strong>What You'll Do 📝:</strong></p><ul><li>Represent the Client's Company by Promoting Their Products / Services</li><li>Raise Brand Awareness & Leave the Customers with 100% Positive Impression</li><li>Work Closely with the Team to Meet (or even, Exceed) the Sales Target</li></ul><p><strong>🔥 Who We're Looking For 🔥:</strong></p><ul><li>Confident Communicator that Loves Networking</li><li>Student Mentality with a Passion for Learning & Growing</li><li>Self-Driven Individual who Enjoys Working in a Team Setting</li></ul><p>⭐️ <strong>What You’ll Get ⭐️:</strong></p><ul><li>📈 <u><em>Advancement</em></u>: Brand Ambassador to Team Leader to Manager to Business Partner [At Your Own Speed]</li><li>👩🏽‍🤝‍👨🏼 <u><em>Culture & Environment</em></u>: Fun & Motivating Team Culture that Celebrates Every Wins [Big or Small]</li><li>🌍 <u><em>Exposure</em></u>: Travelling Opportunities [Road Trips, Office Visits; Learn from Various Performing Individuals]</li><li>🫱🏻‍🫲🏽 <u><em>Mentorship</em></u>: 1-1 Mentorship Throughout to Ensure Continuous Personal & Business Development [Communication Skills, People Skills, Mentality etc.]</li></ul><p><br /><strong>No Experience? No Problem.</strong> If you’re eager to learn and ready to make your mark, we want to hear from you!</p><p><strong>📩 Apply Now and Take the First Step towards an Exciting Future!</strong></p>",
